SCHEMA: infrastructure/formalization_target.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.infrastructure.formalization_target
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Registry entry for infrastructure formalization target kinds.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record formalization_target
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - target_id: id
    - description: string
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- Targets are registry-driven and domain-agnostic.
